{"tid":368841,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲吳宜樺清新性感擠身試鏡行列","createTime":"2017-08-21T23:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T05:14:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b65577fff576adff7677e6568d3cf0a88df3402","tid":368841,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-1-cOrlQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-1-cOrlQ.jpg&h=2c4870cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新星超模吳宜樺人美身材好，私服風格更是十分受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n17歲時一舉奪下新絲路模特兒大賽冠軍，19歲再登上義大利超模之路－羅倫模特大賽冠軍寶座的台灣時尚新星吳宜樺，不僅於2016年成為國際彩妝品牌媚比琳（Maybelline）首位亞洲模特兒，2017年更簽進韓國模特兒公司YGK+，年紀輕輕即在時尚圈大放異彩。更厲害的是，近日吳宜樺現身紐約參與維多利亞的秘密（Victoria&rsquo;s Secret）天使超模試鏡，消息一出吸引眾多粉絲為她集氣加油，期待吳宜樺能成為首位站上夢幻舞台的台灣天使。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-2-1TT0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-2-1TT0Y.jpg&h=087e084b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳宜樺在社群網站上PO出於紐約試鏡維密大秀的街拍美照。<br />\n<br />\n身高177公分，擁有10頭身完美比例的吳宜樺，身形纖細高挑，擁有一雙登天鉛筆腿，更令人羨慕的是，她的上圍也十分豐滿，光是看私服及海邊戲水照就能看出，曲線性感的她若是走上維密大秀，一定能展現出清新又性感的新鮮面貌。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-3-AEuNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-3-AEuNa.jpg&h=10954ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身形纖細的吳宜樺，曲線依舊十分性感。<br />\n<br />\n除了在時尚伸展台及國際品牌的廣告中可以看見吳怡樺的身影，和一般年輕女孩一樣喜愛透過社群網站分享日常點滴的她，也時常PO出穿搭照展現時髦品味。究竟哪些單品是這位新生代超模的最愛、怎麼穿才能又韓又潮，吳宜樺的社群網站上提供了許多參考範本！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-4-Vz1xd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-4-Vz1xd.jpg&h=34d04a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳宜樺自2016年起成為Maybelline首位亞洲模特兒，期間不斷推出不同系列的形象廣告，展現出她多變的時尚面貌。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>寬鬆素面長版上衣</strong><br />\n<br />\n吳宜樺的私服穿搭偏向街頭休閒風格，且愛用極簡元素混搭輕鬆氛圍。寬鬆素面長版上衣搭配非常簡單，不僅可以運用色彩展現甜美、清新、率性等多種面貌，下半身只要套上一件短褲就能展現美腿優勢，不必刻意搶鏡就能奪走旁人目光。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-5-pR4Pf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-5-pR4Pf.jpg&h=ffa95752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-6-1GFaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-6-1GFaS.jpg&h=f1743db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>迷你百褶裙</strong><br />\n<br />\n韓國女星及偶像最愛的迷你百褶裙，也曾多次出現在吳宜樺私服造型中。充滿個性的她巧妙混搭運動風、街頭感單品，將可愛氣息強烈的迷你裙穿出Girl Crush味道，連女生看了都忍不住按讚！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-7-CjVKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-7-CjVKt.jpg&h=2ac0e3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-8-FuvBD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-8-FuvBD.jpg&h=bfcaf6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>全身單一色系穿搭</strong><br />\n<br />\n吳宜樺另一個最受到喜愛的搭配方式，就是統一全身色系，以全黑、全白、全米等色彩完成簡約造型，而且，比起花花綠綠的女孩感元素，這樣的搭配更適合高挑的她！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-9-OjAyQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-9-OjAyQ.jpg&h=9072e513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2017/08/21/170821-6155-10-ddjz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F170821-6155-10-ddjz5.jpg&h=d8796320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://istyle.ltn.com.tw/article/6155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fistyle.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F6155&d=Yugg0IjEz993OydPS6WIcP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=568f4e2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fistyle.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F6155&h=d4a3bc23\" target=\"_blank\">http://istyle.ltn.com.tw/article/6155</a>"},{"pid":"7d7e4f9feadee7cad3c2de339528975b2cfdf9b9","tid":368841,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:54:19.000Z","msg":"對腳瘦到咁樣，靚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1bb63d29f6966aabf673f9e2331c97bf7b12c3","tid":368841,"uid":3649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:23:12.000Z","msg":"普通Model樣，係177cm所以屈機<br />\n<br />\n真係講唔出靚，<br />\n瘦成咁仲話靚根本係病態，<br />\n國際對模特兒嘅審美觀同要求根本痴撚線<br />\n唔值得吹奏<br />\n<br />\n不過有排台灣傳媒講，又黎台灣之光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffee304935024d04d77f6d93d0b8ceef94e19b3","tid":368841,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌骨"},{"pid":"260ddf97690e082fdd83906b6c96be6f1fa514d6","tid":368841,"uid":3305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"對腳好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97837998b4d1418abb9bfd329b75872b5c0ad5ed","tid":368841,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"佢個比例點解咁怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3861a3c1d85ee56cdc979dd5caef6a4846ad4